Doc: A complex type to specify the strike of a credit swaption or a credit default swap option.

Source.Contents:
/#
   A complex type to specify the strike of a credit swaption or a credit default swap option.
 #/
record FpML5.transparency.CreditOptionStrike {
  # The strike of a credit default swap option or credit swaption when expressed as a spread per annum.
  spread : decimal

  # The strike of a credit default swap option or credit swaption when expressed as in reference to the price of the underlying obligation(s) or index.
  price : decimal

  # The strike of a credit default swap option or credit swaption when expressed in reference to the spread of the underlying swap (typical practice in the case of single name swaps).
  strikeReference : FpML5.transparency.FixedRateReference

}

spread.Doc: The strike of a credit default swap option or credit swaption when expressed as a spread per annum.
spread.Name: spread

price.Doc: The strike of a credit default swap option or credit swaption when expressed as in reference to the price of the underlying obligation(s) or index.
price.Name: price

strikeReference.Doc: The strike of a credit default swap option or credit swaption when expressed in reference to the spread of the underlying swap (typical practice in the case of single name swaps).
strikeReference.Name: strikeReference
